        "subject": "Revert \"LU-10461 tests: call exit in the skip routine\"",
        "message": "Revert \"LU-10461 tests: call exit in the skip routine\"\n\nThis reverts commit 33aad7829de56353cca5bbd082d95d6821a7be9c.\n\nconf-sanity tests 32a and 32d are failing for ZFS testing. Reverting this patch to see if adding the return/exit to skip() has an impact on these tests.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=conf-sanity clientdistro=el7 serverdistro=el7 osscount=1 ostcount=2 mdscount=1 mdtcount=1 clientcount=2 ostfilesystemtype=zfs mdtfilesystemtype=zfs\n\nChange-Id: Ifcc3638d7434ca1856a294f08724ef0e26ddf38b\nSigned-off-by:James Nunez <james.a.nunez@intel.com>\n"
      },
